Organized as aesthetic philosophy → technical mastery → occasion application. Unlike competitor "basic how-to" structure, we position jelly nails as a *refinement choice* requiring opacity judgment and intentional layering. Moves from conceptual understanding to hands-on technique to situational styling. Emphasizes control and intentionality over "anything goes translucency."

